items.text: Give unto the LORD, O ye mighty, give unto the LORD glory and strength.
items.plainText: Give unto the LORD, O ye mighty, give unto the LORD glory and strength.

items.text: Give unto the LORD the glory due unto his name; worship the LORD in the beauty of holiness.
items.plainText: Give unto the LORD the glory due unto his name; worship the LORD in the beauty of holiness.

items.text: The voice of the LORD is upon the waters: the God of glory thundereth: the LORD is upon many waters.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD is upon the waters: the God of glory thundereth: the LORD is upon many waters.

items.text: The voice of the LORD is powerful; the voice of the LORD is full of majesty.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD is powerful; the voice of the LORD is full of majesty.

items.text: The voice of the LORD breaketh the cedars; yea, the LORD breaketh the cedars of Lebanon.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD breaketh the cedars; yea, the LORD breaketh the cedars of Lebanon.

items.text: He maketh them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young unicorn.
items.plainText: He maketh them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young unicorn.

items.text: The voice of the LORD divideth the flames of fire.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD divideth the flames of fire.

items.text: The voice of the LORD shaketh the wilderness; the LORD shaketh the wilderness of Kadesh.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD shaketh the wilderness; the LORD shaketh the wilderness of Kadesh.

items.text: The voice of the LORD maketh the hinds to calve, and discovereth the forests: and in his temple doth every one speak of his glory.
items.plainText: The voice of the LORD maketh the hinds to calve, and discovereth the forests: and in his temple doth every one speak of his glory.

items.text: The LORD sitteth upon the flood; yea, the LORD sitteth King for ever.
items.plainText: The LORD sitteth upon the flood; yea, the LORD sitteth King for ever.

items.text: The LORD will give strength unto his people; the LORD will bless his people with peace.
items.plainText: The LORD will give strength unto his people; the LORD will bless his people with peace.
